Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:03.60,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Čast mi je.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:08.39,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Niko ti ne zavidi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:09.52,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dakle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.11,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Ekstravagantan put od četiri dana i tri noći!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.94,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Evo nas, pusto ostrvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:16.07,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigurno nas nešto zabavno čeka tamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.47,0:02:19.74,HaruhiDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Moja uloga je već odlučena, u redu?
